id=update_blocker
name=Update Blocker
version=v1.1
versionCode=2
author=RAFSuNX
description=Blocks Android OTA updates at the root level on Pixel (verified on panther, Android 14, AP2A.240905.003). Nulls out /system/bin/update_engine (the A/B payload applier) and disables the standalone Factory OTA app after boot. Deliberately does not touch GMS/GSF. Requires the OverlayFS MetaModule (meta-overlayfs). Use the KernelSU Manager "Action" button to reset update_engine status and clear cached OTA payloads on demand.
